last_episode_to_air.name: Jaws and Pants Are Dropping
last_episode_to_air.overview: The first elimination sends shock waves, forcing our competitors to pull out the big guns. Plus, Fiona makes an interesting point, Gus bares it all, and Michael shows us what he's learned as a father.

name: Last Laugh
overview: Funhaus, Achievement Hunter, and Rooster Teeth are sending their top comedians to the ultimate challenge. Armed only with a duffel bag of props and their wit, the battle is on to be the last contestant standing - without laughing, while host and referee Geoff Ramsey watches on.
